OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChilly start, with morning fog
OL,6,Fpatches quickly clearing. For most it
OL,7,Fwill be a sunny day. The risk of a few
OL,8,Fshowers through the English Channel.
OL,9,FFeeling warm for many, though chilly
OL,10,Falong eastern coasts. Gusty winds in
OL,11,Fthe south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with clear skies for
OL,14,Fmost. Cloudier across the far
OL,15,Fsouthwest, with the risk of showers
OL,16,Fdeveloping here. Local frost and fog
OL,17,Fin the north. Staying windy in the
OL,18,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
