OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother warm and sunny day
OL,6,Ffor most. Cloudier skies towards
OL,7,Fsouthwestern areas and also Northern
OL,8,FIreland later, with the risk of a few
OL,9,Fshowers developing. Staying windy in
OL,10,Fthe south.
